Name: Average time from 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' to 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' to 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Total time for 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' to reach 'Payment Handled'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Minimum time from 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' to 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average waiting time to the 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' after 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Total resolution time of 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR and the end of the case

Name: Average time it takes 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' after 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Minimum time for 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' to be followed by any approval activity
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Time until 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' from the start of the process
Metric: The sum of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Total time it takes from 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' to 'Request Payment'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' to 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' in cases of rejections
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time for 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' in processes involving 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' and the end of case where activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER occurs

Name: Average time for 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' in cases leading to 'Payment Handled' without rejections
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Payment Handled'
